02:22.343 --> 02:23.311
Marius.

02:23.377 --> 02:25.179
Come on, Marius.

02:30.184 --> 02:32.954
Jim Brown was number 32 in Cleveland

02:33.021 --> 02:35.223
and 44 at Syracuse.

02:35.289 --> 02:38.192
Syracuse and Cleveland it was.

02:38.259 --> 02:40.228
You know he was also a
great lacrosse player?

02:40.294 --> 02:41.930
Maybe you pushed Vince
too hard back there?

02:41.930 --> 02:44.598
He's gonna call before we get in the cab.

02:44.665 --> 02:46.767
- Okay.
- Come on, man.

02:46.834 --> 02:48.402
- Wait, wait, wait, wait, wait, wait, wait.
- [phone rings]

02:48.469 --> 02:49.803
Yeah.

02:49.938 --> 02:51.039
Okay.

02:52.806 --> 02:54.708
He's in for a hundred.

02:54.775 --> 02:56.477
False alarm, buddy.

03:16.917 --> 03:18.238
_

03:24.038 --> 03:25.439
[floor creaks]

04:02.776 --> 04:04.312
[engine starts]

04:36.244 --> 04:37.178
Hey.

04:58.066 --> 04:59.133
Psst.

04:59.200 --> 05:02.136
- Hey.
- Motherfucker!

05:03.071 --> 05:04.572
God damn it.

05:10.111 --> 05:11.079
You okay?

05:11.145 --> 05:13.381
Yeah. Just a leg cramp.

05:14.615 --> 05:15.849
You like what you see?

05:15.916 --> 05:17.651
Yeah. Oh. Uh, no.

05:17.718 --> 05:19.553
- Get out.
- Uh...

05:19.620 --> 05:20.588
Out.

05:25.826 --> 05:27.128
Towel.

05:33.901 --> 05:35.569
You don't get to see this anymore.

05:38.106 --> 05:40.108
You got this place all to yourself?

05:40.108 --> 05:42.876
Yeah. Vince makes a call, they open up.

05:42.943 --> 05:44.612
His games go all night.

05:44.678 --> 05:45.979
Sometimes I need a break

05:46.114 --> 05:47.915
from all those assholes leering at me,

05:47.981 --> 05:49.550
like you're doing right now.

05:49.617 --> 05:50.651
Where's Eddie?

05:50.718 --> 05:52.019
Running the big table.

05:52.120 --> 05:53.754
Oh, he doesn't know he's a prisoner?

05:53.821 --> 05:55.489
No.

05:55.556 --> 05:56.957
Really?

05:57.024 --> 05:58.459
Not yet.

05:59.893 --> 06:01.729
Vince has a big player.

06:01.795 --> 06:03.564
He's ahead,
and Eddie's his favorite dealer.

06:03.631 --> 06:05.333
Why do you want to know where Eddie is?

06:05.399 --> 06:07.901
Are you thinking of grabbing him?

06:07.968 --> 06:10.304
Vince has Richard on Eddie.

06:10.371 --> 06:12.506
He doesn't let him out of his sight.

06:12.573 --> 06:14.442
Why does Vince have
his guys looking for me?

06:14.508 --> 06:16.244
- You ran before.
- Vince doesn't want to hurt me.

06:16.310 --> 06:17.711
Well, he wants to know where you are.

06:17.778 --> 06:19.547
Winslow, however, he wants to kill you.

06:19.613 --> 06:22.150
Vince is not gonna
let Winslow do anything.

06:22.150 --> 06:23.617
Oh, yeah? You don't think

06:23.684 --> 06:25.686
Winslow can come up with an excuse,

06:25.753 --> 06:28.021
say that you went for a gun?

06:28.156 --> 06:30.624
How are you gonna get a
hundred thousand in a week?

06:30.691 --> 06:32.493
I've pulled down more than that before.

06:32.560 --> 06:34.828
Yeah, with a crew and a solid play.

06:34.895 --> 06:37.665
You at least got a place to lay low,
work the cash?

06:37.731 --> 06:40.801
I got a place. I don't know
how much cash I can get.

06:40.868 --> 06:42.636
They have a safe, but...

06:42.703 --> 06:45.339
as far as I know, it's collecting dust.

06:45.406 --> 06:46.974
I'm surprised you didn't just run.

06:47.040 --> 06:48.209
Oh, without Eddie?

06:48.276 --> 06:49.743
Karolina, he's my brother.

06:49.810 --> 06:53.381
You wanted to know where Eddie is.
Now you know.

06:53.447 --> 06:55.416
If you'll excuse me, I need to relax.

06:55.483 --> 06:58.419
I also wanted to see you.

06:58.486 --> 07:00.221
Really?

07:00.288 --> 07:01.755
Did you ever stop to think

07:01.822 --> 07:03.724
about what happened to Charlie
could have happened to me?

07:03.791 --> 07:05.793
Every second, everyday.

07:07.761 --> 07:09.630
Did you talk to Marjorie?

07:09.697 --> 07:12.566
Three fucking years I survived.

07:12.633 --> 07:15.403
I'm not going to risk that.

07:17.871 --> 07:20.874
You have ten seconds before
I start yelling again.

07:26.747 --> 07:29.383
- What country are you from?
- Fuck you.

07:29.450 --> 07:31.285
You could have said Poland.

07:32.853 --> 07:35.223
Don't tell Vince I was here.

